If you're passionate about developing awesome software and would like to join
a friendly, highly capable team - then you need to apply now! This team is
small, diverse and moves fast.

zencontrol is a leader in smart building solutions, renowned for integrating
cutting-edge technology into user-friendly systems. We are looking for an
adept Mobile Application Developer to become part of our Brisbane team,
specializing in iOS/Swift and possessing some understanding of Kotlin, Jetpack
Compose, and Kotlin Multiplatform.

This could be your chance to work in a close-knit team, with people who are
proud of the projects they're working on. The focus is to produce high
quality, working and tested code, which not only keeps everyone happy and
productive but also helps the business to succeed. The development process has
been honed through exploring various flavours.

  
** Responsibilities: **

  * Design, develop, and maintain state-of-the-art applications for both iOS and Android platforms 
  * Utilize Jetpack compose or compose multiplatform. 
  * Collaborate with cross-functional teams to conceptualize, design, and launch innovative features on iOS and/or Android. 
  * Utilize UI testing and API Testing with Mocks and Stubs. 
  * Integration with physical hardware via bluetooth and collaboration with other teams cloud services 
  * Troubleshoot and fix application bottlenecks and bugs. 

** Requirements: **

  * Proficiency with iOS and some experience with Android is an advantage. 
  * Experience with Kotlin. 
  * Proficiency with Jetpack compose or compose multiplatform. 
  * Familiar with CI/CD, Git, TDD/BDD as well as various design patterns such as MVVM 
  * Familiarity with modern UI/UX principles. 
  * In depth proficient knowledge of practices like SOLID, DRY and KISS 
  * Proactive, goal-oriented, energetic and independent way of working 
  * Fluent in English 

** Benefits: **

  * A competitive remuneration package 
  * Opportunity to shape the mobile development team 
  * Creative and innovative work culture 
  * Flexible working arrangements - Hybrid work 
  * Professional development opportunities 

If you have a project where your code is public, please share this in your
resume as it will help you stand out in the crowd.

Visit our website www.zencontrol.com to learn more  

